{
  "stem": "21582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I actually jumped a little bit ahead of myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think around 1942-- and I am not exactly sure about the dates, but approximately-- there was-- apparently the Germans decided that it was time to liquidate the death box.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they went about it very systematically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Up until then, there was attrition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People just died by attrition, and it was quite rapid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after-- at, at that point, we had regular raids where people were just scooped up from the streets and just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Certainly we did not trust it, but we hoped against hope.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, they probably take them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They need people to-- for labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in a way, I think they tried to spread the rumor, oh, that we are taking you just for labor, to labor camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But raids-- the way the raids occurred was that they would come, like, I guess, with a battalion of Germans, I think assisted by, by Lithuanians and Ukrainian followers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But mostly, mostly, I remember German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no way for us to really distinguish them except that they did wear different uniforms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They did not wear the, the the-- I guess auxiliary-- the soldiers that were Russian-- I mean that were Ukrainian or Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember seeing any Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were dressed differently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I am not even absolutely clear that I have seen them, their presence, in, in the ghetto, because I-- their presence was very, very clear in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it's possible that in my memory, that there is-- that there is some, you know, just merging.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it may not be absolutely accurate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the way they did it with, with, with precise suddenness.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would just appear, where we did not have a chance to hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
